data.description: Prime Location Near Dutchess Community College and Marist College. Welcome to this inviting home situated in a highly sought-after location, directly across the street from Dutchess Community College. Nestled in a serene neighborhood setting, this property offers convenience and tranquility while being just minutes away from the vibrant downtown Poughkeepsie area.This home boasts modern amenities, including mini split AC units and solar panels, ensuring comfort and energy efficiency throughout the year. Recently re-done and updated, both bathrooms exude contemporary style and functionality. Step out from the dining room onto the charming back deck, providing an ideal space for outdoor dining, entertaining, or simply unwinding on summer nights. The layout features three generously sized bedrooms, with the primary bedroom offering the convenience of a connecting door to the main bathroom. Downstairs, discover additional living space with a full bathroom, laundry room, and a versatile flex room suitable for various purposes such as a home office, sitting area, or second living room. The attached two-car garage, accessible from the lower level, provides ample parking and storage space.  With its desirable location, and versatile layout, this home presents a remarkable opportunity to be your next home.   Don't miss the chance to make it yours call today to schedule a showing!
